1
00:00:11,500 --> 00:00:13,620
[Payer: Zhong Ning]

2
00:00:15,560 --> 00:00:18,180
Brain gliomas are classified
into four grades.

3
00:00:18,180 --> 00:00:19,210
Grade I is the least severe,

4
00:00:19,210 --> 00:00:21,140
while Grade IV is the most serious.

5
00:00:21,210 --> 00:00:23,210
Your daughter has a Grade IV glioma.

6
00:00:23,680 --> 00:00:25,380
It's highly malignant,

7
00:00:25,400 --> 00:00:26,800
with a poor prognosis.

8
00:00:26,920 --> 00:00:29,250
And it's located in a very difficult area,

9
00:00:29,430 --> 00:00:31,830
which makes the surgery very challenging.

10
00:00:47,070 --> 00:00:49,430
Right now, our last hope

11
00:00:49,890 --> 00:00:52,200
lies with my student, Liao Boyan.

12
00:00:53,370 --> 00:00:56,490
He's one of the world's top neurosurgeons.

13
00:00:56,560 --> 00:00:58,020
He's been working abroad.

14
00:00:58,840 --> 00:01:01,710
He came back for an academic conference
a few days ago.

15
00:01:01,710 --> 00:01:04,069
I've shown him your daughter's case file.

16
00:01:05,150 --> 00:01:07,100
If even he is not confident,

17
00:01:08,430 --> 00:01:09,220
then...

18
00:01:16,510 --> 00:01:18,460
Where is Mom?

19
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:20,620
She is on a business trip.

20
00:01:23,750 --> 00:01:25,890
When will she be back?

21
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:29,120
When you recover and get discharged

22
00:01:29,390 --> 00:01:30,450
from the hospital,

23
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,870
she will be back.

24
00:01:33,320 --> 00:01:34,120
Okay?

25
00:01:34,150 --> 00:01:34,740
Okay.

26
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:08,550
[The Perfect Suspect]

27
00:03:09,660 --> 00:03:12,450
[Episode 4]

28
00:03:12,870 --> 00:03:13,710
[Nanying Hospital of Xinggang City]

29
00:03:13,710 --> 00:03:15,650
Aunt Zhang, I'm sorry.

30
00:03:16,230 --> 00:03:17,710
I lied to you that day.

31
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:21,220
But what I want is the same
as what you want—

32
00:03:21,430 --> 00:03:22,840
to uncover the truth

33
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:25,079
and get justice for your family.

34
00:03:25,190 --> 00:03:26,120
Thank you

35
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:28,680
for saving my life,

36
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:34,320
so I can live to see that justice.

37
00:03:37,079 --> 00:03:39,280
Aunt Zhang, rest assured.

38
00:03:39,550 --> 00:03:41,400
Justice will come.

39
00:03:42,430 --> 00:03:45,470
By the way, we've fixed the photo

40
00:03:45,470 --> 00:03:47,470
you broke that day.

41
00:03:47,470 --> 00:03:48,600
We got it a new frame.

42
00:03:55,990 --> 00:03:56,780
I'll...

43
00:03:57,430 --> 00:03:58,520
I'll put it here.

44
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:04,620
Aunt Zhang,

45
00:04:05,630 --> 00:04:08,750
do you remember the song Hide and Seek?

46
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,470
Youmo and Lijuan

47
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:13,560
used to play it for Tong often.

48
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:15,240
Was there anything unusual

49
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,769
when they played this song?

50
00:04:19,070 --> 00:04:21,529
What could be unusual
about a nursery rhyme?

51
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:26,250
I've read the interrogation records.

52
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:28,450
You told the police

53
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,830
Zhao Qian ruined Yang Youmo's family.

54
00:04:30,830 --> 00:04:31,750
But there's one question

55
00:04:31,750 --> 00:04:33,950
that you have never answered directly.

56
00:04:34,450 --> 00:04:36,180
What was Yang Youmo's attitude

57
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:38,310
towards Zhao Qian?

58
00:04:40,990 --> 00:04:42,580
Zhao Qian said

59
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:46,240
Yang Youmo had feelings for her,

60
00:04:47,490 --> 00:04:50,240
but she only saw him as a friend.

61
00:04:51,030 --> 00:04:52,690
That's a lie. That's a lie!

62
00:04:52,760 --> 00:04:54,740
That's a lie! It was not like that!

63
00:04:54,760 --> 00:04:55,700
That's a lie.

64
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:57,690
It was not like that.

65
00:04:57,909 --> 00:04:58,710
Calm down.

66
00:04:59,260 --> 00:05:01,500
So we need you to tell us the truth.

67
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:06,480
The truth...

68
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:11,870
[Temporary Construction Waste Site]

69
00:05:15,740 --> 00:05:17,540
Don't embarrass yourself here.

70
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:27,670
Since your life is so miserable,

71
00:05:28,620 --> 00:05:30,340
why don't you just end it?

72
00:05:52,630 --> 00:05:53,490
Lijuan.

73
00:05:55,230 --> 00:05:56,680
Are you alright?

74
00:05:57,530 --> 00:05:58,400
Lijuan.

75
00:05:59,650 --> 00:06:01,170
Don't cry.

76
00:06:01,850 --> 00:06:04,320
So during Luo Lijuan's pregnancy,

77
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:06,970
Yang Youmo was already with Zhao Qian?

78
00:06:15,700 --> 00:06:19,900
They used to be such a loving couple.

79
00:06:21,690 --> 00:06:23,540
It was all because of Zhao Qian.

80
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,640
It was all Zhao Qian's fault.

81
00:06:26,280 --> 00:06:28,610
You're here to harass my aunt again?

82
00:06:29,690 --> 00:06:32,090
Fine. You want her dead. Is that so?

83
00:06:32,090 --> 00:06:32,159
[Recording]

84
00:06:32,159 --> 00:06:34,120
Because of your incompetence,

85
00:06:34,140 --> 00:06:36,250
the murderer is still free.

86
00:06:36,310 --> 00:06:37,560
She almost died!

87
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:38,240
Who are you?

88
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:40,750
I'm a citizen. An internet celebrity.

89
00:06:41,010 --> 00:06:41,070
[Recording]

90
00:06:41,070 --> 00:06:44,190
We're the police.
We're conducting a lawful interrogation.

91
00:06:44,190 --> 00:06:45,390
Please don't interfere
with our investigation.

92
00:06:45,390 --> 00:06:47,000
We netizens also have the right to know.

93
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,070
You must explain everything clearly today.

94
00:06:48,070 --> 00:06:49,120
-Please leave.
-Please leave.

95
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:50,190
No. We'll talk here.

96
00:06:50,190 --> 00:06:51,070
Don't be unreasonable.

97
00:06:51,070 --> 00:06:51,950
We'll talk here.

98
00:06:51,950 --> 00:06:52,870
Do you understand?

99
00:06:52,870 --> 00:06:54,070
Everyone, see?

100
00:06:54,070 --> 00:06:55,680
This is how the police handle cases.

101
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:57,210
This is how they protect us!

102
00:07:41,750 --> 00:07:42,750
You're not paying again.

103
00:07:42,750 --> 00:07:43,670
I already paid.

104
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,070
You didn't.

105
00:07:45,390 --> 00:07:46,350
I just did.

106
00:07:46,430 --> 00:07:47,750
What are you doing?
Why are you pulling me?

107
00:07:47,750 --> 00:07:49,360
-You didn't pay!
-I did!

108
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:50,710
Why are you doing this?

109
00:07:50,830 --> 00:07:52,310
Why are you always like this?

110
00:07:52,310 --> 00:07:53,070
Compensate me!

111
00:07:53,070 --> 00:07:54,130
You compensate me!

112
00:07:54,310 --> 00:07:56,560
God. Go see a doctor if you're sick, okay?

113
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,310
I can't believe you.

114
00:07:57,310 --> 00:07:58,310
You're still taking my things!

115
00:07:58,310 --> 00:08:00,110
You have to pay for what you take!

116
00:08:00,510 --> 00:08:01,920
-I already paid!
-Stop!

117
00:08:04,870 --> 00:08:05,750
I'll pay.

118
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,190
50 yuan.

119
00:08:50,870 --> 00:08:51,670
Dr. Liao.

120
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:56,670
I'm Zhong Renxi's father,

121
00:08:56,770 --> 00:08:57,670
Zhong Ning.

122
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,400
Do you still remember me?

123
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:02,970
Seven years ago,

124
00:09:04,790 --> 00:09:06,200
you saved Renxi's life.

125
00:09:10,260 --> 00:09:11,260
I don't remember.

126
00:09:39,090 --> 00:09:41,830
[No Parking in Fire Lane]

127
00:09:48,230 --> 00:09:49,290
[No Parking in Fire Lane]

128
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:50,670
Enough.

129
00:10:12,550 --> 00:10:14,270
You're not lying to me, are you?

130
00:10:14,270 --> 00:10:15,790
I wouldn't dare.

131
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:19,150
I'm really tracking down that drug buyer.

132
00:10:19,150 --> 00:10:20,210
Have you found him?

133
00:10:20,310 --> 00:10:20,970
Soon.

134
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:23,000
Soon. Soon.

135
00:10:36,040 --> 00:10:36,850
Three days.

136
00:10:38,230 --> 00:10:39,940
I give you three days.

137
00:10:41,050 --> 00:10:42,490
Three days. Okay.

138
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:03,720
What's wrong?

139
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:06,120
I feel unwell.

140
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,750
You're unwell? I'm unwell too!

141
00:11:13,090 --> 00:11:14,290
Go buy some medicine!

142
00:11:15,100 --> 00:11:16,530
Useless idiot.

143
00:11:19,500 --> 00:11:22,010
[Agreement for Paid Corneal Donation]

144
00:11:22,040 --> 00:11:23,910
[Party A's signature: Zhang Jiajun
Party B's signature: Xie Wuqiang]

145
00:11:31,390 --> 00:11:32,760
Where are his parents?

146
00:11:32,870 --> 00:11:34,210
Why did he faint?

147
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:35,150
You don't know him either?

148
00:11:35,150 --> 00:11:36,140
I don't know him.

149
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,760
Call an ambulance!

150
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:40,950
Wake up, child. Wake up.

151
00:11:41,390 --> 00:11:42,460
What happened?

152
00:11:42,550 --> 00:11:43,870
Hello, are you the emergency center?

153
00:11:43,870 --> 00:11:44,720
He fainted?

154
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:46,210
A child fainted.

155
00:11:48,550 --> 00:11:49,480
Stop the car!

156
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:18,150
I'm here to thank you.

157
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:19,910
Um... my wife

158
00:13:19,930 --> 00:13:21,200
told me that someone sent my son

159
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:21,650
to the hospital

160
00:13:21,650 --> 00:13:22,150
[No Spitting
No Littering]

161
00:13:22,150 --> 00:13:23,670
and even paid the medical expenses.

162
00:13:23,670 --> 00:13:25,360
You hid it so well.

163
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:29,960
You don't look like a rich man,

164
00:13:29,980 --> 00:13:31,750
but you paid the medical fees generously.

165
00:13:31,750 --> 00:13:33,310
Why don't you be more generous?

166
00:13:33,310 --> 00:13:35,080
Give me a few hundred thousand yuan

167
00:13:35,080 --> 00:13:37,080
and help my son get a kidney transplant.

168
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:37,700
Thank you.

169
00:13:45,800 --> 00:13:47,200
Still playing dumb, huh?

170
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:51,050
Don't make me
bring in someone else to talk to you.

171
00:13:51,150 --> 00:13:52,840
Do you know Kai—Liu Renkai?

172
00:13:54,070 --> 00:13:56,170
He's not as polite as I am.

173
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:59,080
What exactly do you want?

174
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:04,270
I want to help you...

175
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:07,240
hide a murder.

176
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,440
You killed someone?

177
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,600
You killed someone!

178
00:14:09,630 --> 00:14:10,960
You killed someone!

179
00:14:21,010 --> 00:14:21,610
I...

180
00:14:26,080 --> 00:14:28,010
I don't believe you won't confess!

181
00:14:33,580 --> 00:14:35,750
[Nanying Hospital of Xinggang City]

182
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:38,600
Make sure he gets enough sleep at night.

183
00:14:38,600 --> 00:14:39,930
Keep him well hydrated.

184
00:14:39,960 --> 00:14:41,630
Have a proper talk with his family.

185
00:14:41,630 --> 00:14:42,120
Okay.

186
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:44,120
Hello, President Cao.

187
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:45,510
I'm Zhong Ning.

188
00:14:45,510 --> 00:14:46,910
Do you still remember me?

189
00:14:47,480 --> 00:14:48,270
Zhong.

190
00:14:50,510 --> 00:14:52,240
I want to ask you about someone.

191
00:14:53,150 --> 00:14:54,910
Liao Boyan, your student.

192
00:14:55,510 --> 00:14:56,550
Seven years ago,

193
00:14:56,550 --> 00:14:58,960
he performed brain glioma surgery
on my daughter.

194
00:14:58,960 --> 00:15:00,290
What do you want to know?

195
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,150
Ask away.

196
00:15:01,510 --> 00:15:04,510
Do you know how Dr. Liao is doing now?

197
00:15:04,510 --> 00:15:05,390
Roughly, yes.

198
00:15:05,550 --> 00:15:07,600
How did he end up like this?

199
00:15:09,910 --> 00:15:13,120
You know he had been working abroad.

200
00:15:15,120 --> 00:15:18,200
Five years ago, I persuaded him
to return to China.

201
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:20,120
He was tempted.

202
00:15:20,390 --> 00:15:23,120
He agreed to come back
with his wife and daughter.

203
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:26,480
A few well-known hospitals in China

204
00:15:26,480 --> 00:15:27,870
extended offers to him.

205
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:30,780
But unexpectedly,

206
00:15:37,080 --> 00:15:38,540
his daughter, Liao Yifan,

207
00:15:38,790 --> 00:15:42,050
was hit and killed by a car
right in front of him and his wife.

208
00:15:42,200 --> 00:15:43,820
The driver fled the scene.

209
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:46,600
It's been five years,
and they still haven't caught the person.

210
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:47,600
After that incident,

211
00:15:47,600 --> 00:15:49,770
Liao Boyan's life fell apart.

212
00:15:51,760 --> 00:15:54,220
He developed severe psychological issues.

213
00:15:54,270 --> 00:15:55,530
His wife divorced him.

214
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:58,860
And he was diagnosed
with Alzheimer's disease.

215
00:16:15,510 --> 00:16:16,770
Back then, I made a vow.

216
00:16:19,150 --> 00:16:22,510
Once Zhong Renxi's surgery was a success,

217
00:16:22,930 --> 00:16:24,360
I would go vegetarian.

218
00:16:25,490 --> 00:16:28,160
You ordered so many dishes.

219
00:16:28,320 --> 00:16:29,980
Do you need something from me?

220
00:16:31,390 --> 00:16:33,120
Let's finish this drink first.

221
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:37,380
Everyone else tells me to drink less.

222
00:16:37,750 --> 00:16:39,510
Only you tell me to down it all.

223
00:16:40,270 --> 00:16:42,070
Because I consider you a friend.

224
00:16:43,270 --> 00:16:45,320
I know what you truly want.

225
00:16:47,550 --> 00:16:48,240
What?

226
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:57,060
You want to forget.

227
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:03,510
I already have Alzheimer's.

228
00:17:04,310 --> 00:17:06,440
I don't need alcohol to forget things.

229
00:17:08,720 --> 00:17:09,829
But I want you

230
00:17:10,960 --> 00:17:12,819
to remember the past.

231
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:14,680
And what good would that do?

232
00:17:15,030 --> 00:17:16,720
I'm not a doctor anymore.

233
00:17:16,720 --> 00:17:17,960
I can't help you.

234
00:17:18,069 --> 00:17:19,720
And I'm no longer a cop.

235
00:17:20,550 --> 00:17:23,410
But that doesn't stop me
from investigating cases.

236
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:27,329
In a recent case,

237
00:17:28,440 --> 00:17:29,750
the victim died

238
00:17:29,750 --> 00:17:31,640
from an overdose of adrenaline.

239
00:17:32,400 --> 00:17:35,070
The killer timed the death perfectly.

240
00:17:35,920 --> 00:17:36,920
That means

241
00:17:37,310 --> 00:17:40,510
the murderer had to control the dosage
and the technique precisely.

242
00:17:40,510 --> 00:17:41,510
In other words,

243
00:17:41,920 --> 00:17:42,720
the killer

244
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:44,790
had medical training.

245
00:17:46,160 --> 00:17:48,640
Any doctor could

246
00:17:48,790 --> 00:17:49,720
tell you that.

247
00:17:50,710 --> 00:17:53,450
Why did you come to me, a washed-up man?

248
00:17:54,240 --> 00:17:55,070
Dr. Liao,

249
00:17:56,310 --> 00:17:58,160
I hope this case

250
00:17:59,200 --> 00:18:00,550
can help you get better,

251
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:02,800
so that you can help more people.

252
00:18:03,310 --> 00:18:05,070
You think I'm bored

253
00:18:05,790 --> 00:18:07,720
and want to give me something to do?

254
00:18:08,110 --> 00:18:09,550
You can see it that way.

255
00:18:14,720 --> 00:18:16,480
Your name is Zhong Ning?

256
00:18:17,140 --> 00:18:18,000
Officer Zhong,

257
00:18:19,510 --> 00:18:21,510
why are you so invested in me?

258
00:18:25,200 --> 00:18:26,000
Because...

259
00:18:27,750 --> 00:18:29,160
you helped me before.

260
00:18:30,310 --> 00:18:31,910
And I want to repay the favor.

261
00:18:33,590 --> 00:18:34,590
What's that?

262
00:18:35,440 --> 00:18:37,770
His wife died in an accident
a few days ago.

263
00:18:57,480 --> 00:18:59,010
Mr. Liao, what should we do?

264
00:18:59,110 --> 00:19:00,790
Those vials are imported.

265
00:19:00,810 --> 00:19:02,070
We don't have much stock left.

266
00:19:02,070 --> 00:19:04,390
A few kids are in urgent need of it.

267
00:19:04,510 --> 00:19:05,790
I counted everything carefully

268
00:19:05,790 --> 00:19:07,270
when I left the pharmacy.

269
00:19:07,270 --> 00:19:09,330
By the time I got here, they were gone.

270
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:11,270
You don't work here, so you wouldn't know—

271
00:19:11,270 --> 00:19:14,600
this isn't the first time
something like this has happened.

272
00:19:23,090 --> 00:19:26,310
[Inpatient Area]

273
00:19:26,310 --> 00:19:27,640
You're a police officer.

274
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:28,920
We need your help.

275
00:19:29,480 --> 00:19:30,750
The hospital lost some medicine.

276
00:19:30,750 --> 00:19:32,270
One of them is crucial to kids

277
00:19:32,270 --> 00:19:34,270
and must be used before their surgeries.

278
00:19:34,270 --> 00:19:35,600
Without this medicine,

279
00:19:36,030 --> 00:19:37,560
I can't save your daughter.

280
00:19:41,680 --> 00:19:43,680
The medicine was put here in a row.

281
00:19:43,710 --> 00:19:44,710
But now it's gone.

282
00:19:46,330 --> 00:19:47,150
[Neurology Medication List]

283
00:19:52,510 --> 00:19:54,710
Did you see anyone suspicious going in?

284
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:55,720
No.

285
00:20:08,420 --> 00:20:08,620
[Inpatient Area]

286
00:20:08,620 --> 00:20:10,280
Have you come to a conclusion?

287
00:20:12,270 --> 00:20:13,670
I don't know if it counts.

288
00:20:14,830 --> 00:20:15,920
Tell me.

289
00:20:16,640 --> 00:20:18,160
I asked the nurse on duty

290
00:20:19,830 --> 00:20:22,680
and checked all the surveillance footage

291
00:20:22,680 --> 00:20:24,440
from the pharmacy to the wards.

292
00:20:26,030 --> 00:20:28,090
No one was caught stealing anything.

293
00:20:28,920 --> 00:20:31,950
So I checked the list of drugs.

294
00:20:33,050 --> 00:20:36,440
I found that all the missing drugs
were of the same type.

295
00:20:38,810 --> 00:20:41,820
There were
more expensive drugs on the cart,

296
00:20:42,880 --> 00:20:44,410
but those weren't touched.

297
00:20:46,740 --> 00:20:48,730
Maybe the thief didn't know.

298
00:20:48,760 --> 00:20:50,360
No, he knew exactly what he was doing.

299
00:20:50,360 --> 00:20:52,650
He's an expert in pharmaceuticals.

300
00:20:54,880 --> 00:20:57,090
He can quickly and accurately pick out

301
00:20:57,150 --> 00:20:58,600
the same type of drug

302
00:20:59,350 --> 00:21:00,880
from a pile of medications.

303
00:21:01,440 --> 00:21:02,640
Am I right?

304
00:21:05,610 --> 00:21:06,610
You're asking me?

305
00:21:07,480 --> 00:21:08,960
I can also ask the nurse.

306
00:21:10,030 --> 00:21:11,360
She's your accomplice.

307
00:21:15,550 --> 00:21:17,310
You really are a good cop.

308
00:21:23,160 --> 00:21:24,590
I'm not a cop anymore.

309
00:21:26,750 --> 00:21:28,270
You staged this whole

310
00:21:29,110 --> 00:21:30,960
"a cop catching a thief" act.

311
00:21:31,110 --> 00:21:31,910
Why?

312
00:21:32,740 --> 00:21:33,800
To make a fool of me?

313
00:21:36,070 --> 00:21:37,600
To give you something to do.

314
00:21:38,080 --> 00:21:39,880
To get your brain working again.

315
00:21:43,030 --> 00:21:44,240
I know brains.

316
00:21:45,000 --> 00:21:46,400
Some need surgery.

317
00:21:46,880 --> 00:21:48,030
Some need medicine.

318
00:21:49,070 --> 00:21:52,110
And some need alcohol wrung out of them.

319
00:21:56,090 --> 00:21:57,850
Start over, Zhong Ning.

320
00:21:58,670 --> 00:21:59,760
Start over?

321
00:22:02,240 --> 00:22:03,110
How?

322
00:22:05,640 --> 00:22:07,640
My daughter could die at any moment.

323
00:22:09,110 --> 00:22:10,270
They told me

324
00:22:11,670 --> 00:22:13,670
she has one slim chance of survival.

325
00:22:15,830 --> 00:22:16,830
I will

326
00:22:18,120 --> 00:22:20,010
make sure she gets it.

327
00:22:26,440 --> 00:22:27,500
Once she recovers,

328
00:22:28,030 --> 00:22:30,160
she'll need a father who doesn't drink

329
00:22:30,400 --> 00:22:32,110
and thinks clearly.

330
00:22:52,440 --> 00:22:54,300
You're the only one I can count on.

331
00:23:03,440 --> 00:23:05,300
You didn't just save my daughter.

332
00:23:05,920 --> 00:23:06,850
You saved me too.

333
00:23:09,590 --> 00:23:12,790
Not everyone is willing to face the past.

334
00:23:15,070 --> 00:23:18,750
Now, I wish my condition could get worse.

335
00:23:20,960 --> 00:23:22,960
Do you want to forget your daughter?

336
00:23:24,640 --> 00:23:26,790
We're not on the same page.

337
00:23:30,510 --> 00:23:33,380
Dr. Liao, I understand
what you've been through.

338
00:23:33,400 --> 00:23:35,380
