339
00:23:35,760 --> 00:23:38,000
Now I want the same for you.

340
00:23:38,070 --> 00:23:39,480
If there's anything I can do,

341
00:23:39,480 --> 00:23:40,400
just tell me.

342
00:23:40,400 --> 00:23:41,400
I will try my best.

343
00:23:47,110 --> 00:23:48,160
Understand me?

344
00:23:51,310 --> 00:23:52,710
What gives you the right?

345
00:23:54,510 --> 00:23:57,370
Just because
your daughter, Zhong Renxi, was sick?

346
00:23:58,350 --> 00:23:59,900
She didn't really die.

347
00:24:00,750 --> 00:24:02,510
When Zhong Renxi actually dies,

348
00:24:02,510 --> 00:24:05,040
come back and talk to me
about understanding.

349
00:24:20,310 --> 00:24:21,170
Check, please.

350
00:24:23,490 --> 00:24:25,310
305 yuan. Just give me 300 yuan.

351
00:24:26,310 --> 00:24:27,000
Thank you.

352
00:24:45,280 --> 00:24:47,430
[Math Test for Grade 4, Third Monthly Exam
