362
00:25:45,590 --> 00:25:46,400
It's okay.

363
00:25:53,640 --> 00:25:56,200
Then sign it while you're in a good mood.

364
00:25:57,480 --> 00:25:58,270
Okay.

365
00:26:00,030 --> 00:26:01,880
Actually, when I was a kid,

366
00:26:02,480 --> 00:26:03,940
I only got passing scores.

367
00:26:05,270 --> 00:26:06,790
Dad, if you'd been like this earlier,

368
00:26:06,790 --> 00:26:09,120
I would've been sincere with you long ago.

369
00:26:11,270 --> 00:26:12,480
Let's go eat something tasty?

370
00:26:12,480 --> 00:26:13,010
Let's go.

371
00:26:13,270 --> 00:26:15,200
-Let's go.
-Let's go eat something delicious.

372
00:26:15,200 --> 00:26:17,460
We're going to eat something delicious!

373
00:26:20,680 --> 00:26:23,000
The killer seems to be
in a closed loop of connection

374
00:26:23,000 --> 00:26:24,790
with Zhao Qian and Yang Youmo.

375
00:26:24,790 --> 00:26:26,350
Because this was clearly premeditated.

376
00:26:26,350 --> 00:26:28,000
I believe it was an act of revenge.

377
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:29,880
Why was the killer so twisted?

378
00:26:31,310 --> 00:26:33,680
The killer forced Yang Youmo
into a deadly game

379
00:26:33,680 --> 00:26:37,000
and threw Zhao Qian, who has mysophobia,
into a garbage pit.

380
00:26:37,000 --> 00:26:38,480
It must be deep hatred.

381
00:26:39,310 --> 00:26:39,880
That's why

382
00:26:39,880 --> 00:26:41,510
the killer used such elaborate methods

383
00:26:41,510 --> 00:26:42,310
to commit the crimes.

384
00:26:42,310 --> 00:26:42,970
The purpose

385
00:26:43,030 --> 00:26:46,830
