392
00:26:56,680 --> 00:26:57,790
business competitors,

393
00:26:57,790 --> 00:26:58,830
enemies in trade,

394
00:26:58,830 --> 00:27:00,200
the victim of the traffic accident,

395
00:27:00,200 --> 00:27:02,480
and individuals with personal grudges,
like Fang Qinchun.

396
00:27:02,480 --> 00:27:04,270
-No one seems to be a solid suspect.
-Wait.

397
00:27:04,270 --> 00:27:05,550
What traffic accident?

398
